name: elasticsearch
description:
Elasticsearch is a search engine based on Lucene. It provides a
distributed, multitenant-capable full-text search engine with an HTTP
web interface and schema-free JSON documents.

dependencies.name: java
dependencies.description:
The Java Development Kit (JDK) released by Oracle Corporation in the
form of a binary product aimed at Java developers. Includes a complete
JRE plus tools for developing, debugging, and monitoring Java
applications.
